<li>With deepest sympathy, our hearts go out to you and your family during this difficult time.</li>
<li>May God grant you the strength and peace you need to navigate this profound loss.</li>
<li>Holding you in our thoughts and prayers as you mourn the passing of your beloved .</li>
<li>Your family is in our hearts, may the love surrounding you help ease your sorrow.</li>
<li> May the beautiful memories you shared bring you comfort in the days ahead.</li>
<li>We are so sorry for your loss. May God wrap you in his loving embrace.</li>
<li>Sending you love and strength during this incredibly painful time.</li>
<li>May the Lord comfort you and your family in this time of sorrow.</li>
<li>We offer our deepest condolences on your heartbreaking loss.</li>
<li>May God's grace sustain you and your family through this period of mourning.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family with heartfelt sympathy.</li>
